descriptionHtml:
Nibiru

Nibiru is located on the road east of Dushnikh Yal.  It is companion friendly and can be fast traveled to immediately.  It is script-free, fully navmeshed and has everything most adventurers will need.  The clutter is static so you don\'t have to worry about knocking items around.       


FEATURES:
- Script-Free
- Fully Navmeshed
- Two Bookcases
- Two Mannequins
- Four Display Cases
- Imbuing Station
- All Crafting Stations
- Plenty of Safe Storage


Requirements:

Dragonborn DLC
Skyrim Patch 1.9.32.0.8


Install:

Just copy Nibiru.esp into your Skyrim\\Data\\ folder.


Uninstall:

Just delete Nibiru.esp from your Skyrim\\Data folder.
author: SuperMegaSuperMega
